list.item:
Direct the Commander in Chief, United Nations Command (CINCUNC) to increase immediately the scale
                        of military operations in the Korean campaign to the maximum consistent with
                        the capabilities and security of the forces now available;

Develop and equip dependable ROK military
                        units, as rapidly as possible and in sufficient strength, with a view to
                        their assuming the major responsibility for the defense of Korea;

GA resolution recondemning the aggressor,
reaffirming UN determination to carry on the fight, and requesting further
assistance;

